{"tid":500240,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有隻狗 成班人 一齊去捉鬼","createTime":"2017-12-15T14:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T14:26:01.000Z","uid":16953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"904952927a8013c433242b4e177bb48ab995c631","tid":500240,"uid":16953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"請問哩套係咩片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剩係記得個主角係一大班人連埋隻狗<br />\n有個男嘅好細膽 隻狗都好細膽 佢地成日一齊<br />\n剩係記得哩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有！<br />\n以前睇過1個卡通係明珠台播定有線播<br />\n每集都係個男仔走去秘密基地<br />\n然後入咗部機 送佢去咗個虛擬世界<br />\n佢要喺個虛擬世界打敗個壞人 <br />\n最後每幕都係會放隻手落部機 <br />\n就好似mission clear咁<br />\n哩套又係咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa96c2b21469197e97e1a4df999b853b9bd42fb2","tid":500240,"uid":52020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"叔比狗"},{"pid":"c263fdac57a25a22062c0e16404818d01135e5da","tid":500240,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"汪！汪！！汪！！！"},{"pid":"7bc821c722c9ecee831d8f290fa0f49ee22fcb2c","tid":500240,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"scooby doo"},{"pid":"fd6940fdc4afff951af5a8aef7b7546753ba8538","tid":500240,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"狗狗震多震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66dd337b17efa6367935b64ff90930a9ce814bd","tid":500240,"uid":16953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockq